<codeline lineno="67"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>**Metadata<sp/>Handling**:<sp/>Attempts<sp/>to<sp/>load<sp/>cached<sp/>metadata<sp/>from<sp/>`meta_state.pkl`.<sp/>If<sp/>`FetchMeta`<sp/>is<sp/>enabled,<sp/>it<sp/>fetches<sp/>new<sp/>metadata<sp/>using<sp/>the<sp/>`Meta`<sp/>class<sp/>and<sp/>caches<sp/>it.</highlight></codeline>
